    "Therefore, extracting navigational sequential landmarks is crucial for the landmark discovery.",
    "2) Landmark Cooccurrence: the open-world landmark cooccurrence knowledge, e.g., a counter may appear in a kitchen island (Fig. 2), can greatly help the alignment.",
    "We design customized prompts with heuristic task examples to obtain these two kinds of priors.Navigational Sequential Landmark Extraction.",
    "An ideal extraction of landmarks requires: (1) extraction of all mentioned landmarks; (2) successful extraction of landmarks with complex descriptions (e.g., landmarks with adjectives or phrases); (3) avoidance of abstract nouns (e.g., right); (4) navigational order instead of textual order.",
